snippet.title: NAMCO MUSEUM - Launch Trailer | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
With NAMCO MUSEUM, you can relive the glory days of arcade games anytime, anywhere! 

NAMCO MUSEUM is available on July 28, 2017 for $29.99 exclusively through the Nintendo eShop for the Nintendo Switch. 

Get more info about Namco Museum here:
https://www.bandainamcoent.com/games/namco-museum
